title: Breaking Down Fringe Teams with Baldy, Cowboys-Saints preview
itunes:title: Breaking Down Fringe Teams with Baldy, Cowboys-Saints preview
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal recap the MNF clash (if that's what you want to call it) between the Washington Football Team and Seahawks. Brian Baldinger joins the show to talk about some teams we can't quite figure out and then Colleen Wolfe aka the Tiny Box joins the show to preview the Cowboys at Saints.
